lead_paragraph: Ryan Lochte knew there would be obstacles on his way to qualifying for his fourth Olympics. He just wasn't expecting one while trying to get to the U.S. swimming trials.

headline.main: Flying Low: Lochte Finds Trouble en Route to US Swim Trials
